title.narrative: WC015 Unrestricted Funding from War Child Donors

description.narrative: These funds are primarily used for coordination activities. You can access the funded project(s) by clicking on the family tree links situated underneath this d-portal screen. These links will direct users to a project screen or an empty screen. The latter case relates to coordination activities that are linked to several projects as opposed to one, among others. Updated 2019-11-11
